# V3.1: THE DUAL-PROTOCOL ARCHITECTURE (REST + MCP)

This specification outlines the evolution of the FHIR-MCP-data-bridge into a unified **Clinical Intelligence Hub**. We will expose our underlying clinical logic simultaneously as **FastMCP Tools** (for autonomous AI Agents) and standard **FastAPI REST Endpoints** (designed to power an **EHR Sidecar UI / Ambient Intelligence Module**), ensuring 100% parity, enhanced observability, and unified security. By embedding directly alongside the EHR (e.g., via SMART-on-FHIR), we eliminate context-switching and combat clinician burnout.

