## 5. Parity Testing Suite (Proof of Verification)

| Test Name | Action | Verification Check |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Semantic Parity** | `intelligence.get_semantic_suggestions("Rash")` vs `GET /api/v3/semantic-search?q=Rash` | Verify the Pydantic List elements are exactly identical between protocols. |
| **Cache Hit Parity** | Call `GET /semantic-search?q=Diabetes` twice. | Second call must resolve in < 5ms (Cache Hit). |
| **CORS Validation** | Trigger a `fetch()` from a browser console to the REST endpoint. | Verify `Access-Control-Allow-Origin` is present in headers. |
| **Security Gate** | Call REST endpoint without an API Key. | Must return `403 Forbidden`. |

